### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alexis@example.dev",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

### Me
GET http://localhost:8080/api/me

### Sections
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sections

### Genres
GET http://localhost:8080/api/genres

### Search
GET http://localhost:8080/api/catalog?query=botanical&type=SERIES

### Filter by genre
GET http://localhost:8080/api/catalog?genre=Technologie

### Detail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/catalog/botanical-cities

### Playback metadata
GET http://localhost:8080/api/videos/1

### Stream headers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/videos/1/stream
Range: bytes=0-1023

### HLS playlist
GET http://localhost:8080/api/videos/1/hls/master.m3u8

### HLS segment
GET http://localhost:8080/api/videos/1/hls/segment_000.ts

### Subtitles
GET http://localhost:8080/api/videos/1/subtitles

### Progress
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/videos/1/progress
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "positionSeconds": 7,
  "durationSeconds": 12
}

### Watchlist add
POST http://localhost:8080/api/titles/1/watchlist

### Watchlist remove
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/titles/1/watchlist

### Logout
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/logout
